## Customer Portal 2.0 — HubSpot CMS Build Plan

### Architecture Overview

Based on the [HubSpot/recruiting-agency-graphql-theme](https://github.com/HubSpot/recruiting-agency-graphql-theme) reference (which does *exactly* what you need — membership-gated pages showing per-contact CRM data via GraphQL), here's the full plan.

### Phase 0: Prerequisites & Environment Setup

| Step | Action |
|---|---|
| 0.1 | Install HubSpot CLI: `npm install -g @hubspot/cli` |
| 0.2 | Run `hs init` → paste your PAK → connect your portal |
| 0.3 | Set up a **sandbox account** for development (`hs sandbox create`) |
| 0.4 | Connect a custom subdomain (e.g., `portal.hairsolutions.co`) — required for memberships |

### Phase 1: CRM Custom Object Schemas

Create these via API (`POST /crm/v3/schemas`) — JSON schema files in a `schemas/` directory, same pattern as the recruiting-agency-graphql-theme:

**1.1 `schemas/hair_profile.json`** — Custom Object: Hair Profile
```
Properties: head_circumference (number), front_to_nape (number), ear_to_ear (number),
temple_to_temple (number), preferred_style (text), density (enumeration: light/medium/heavy),
hair_color (text), base_type (enumeration: lace/skin/mono), attachment_method (enumeration: tape/glue/clips),
activity_level (text), sweating_level (enumeration: low/moderate/high),
work_environment (text), sports_activities (text),
photo_front (file), photo_side (file), photo_back (file), photo_top (file),
notes (textarea), onboarding_completed (booleancheckbox)
Associations: CONTACT
Primary display: preferred_style
```

**1.2 `schemas/order.json`** — Custom Object: Order
```
Properties: order_number (text, hasUniqueValue), product_name (text),
status (enumeration: pending/confirmed/in_production/quality_check/shipped/delivered/cancelled),
production_stage (enumeration: awaiting_confirmation/materials_preparation/base_construction/
  hair_ventilation/styling/quality_inspection/packaging/completed),
subtotal (number), tax (number), shipping (number), total (number), currency (text),
estimated_production_start (date), estimated_completion (date),
actual_completion_date (date), shipped_at (date), delivered_at (date),
customer_notes (textarea), configuration_snapshot (textarea)
Associations: CONTACT
Primary display: order_number
```

**1.3 `schemas/order_status_history.json`** — Custom Object: Order Status Update
```
Properties: status (enumeration: same as order), stage (enumeration: same as order),
notes (textarea), created_by (text)
Associations: order (custom object)
Primary display: status
```

**1.4 `schemas/customization_template.json`** — Custom Object: Customization Template
```
Properties: template_name (text), base_type (enumeration: lace/skin/mono),
hair_color (text), density (enumeration: light/medium/heavy),
hair_length (text), style (text), attachment_method (enumeration: tape/glue/clips),
additional_options (textarea), is_default (booleancheckbox), notes (textarea)
Associations: CONTACT
Primary display: template_name
```

**1.5 `schemas/invoice.json`** — Custom Object: Invoice
```
Properties: invoice_number (text, hasUniqueValue), amount (number), tax (number),
total (number), currency (text), status (enumeration: pending/paid/overdue/cancelled),
issue_date (date), due_date (date), paid_at (date), pdf_url (text), description (textarea)
Associations: CONTACT, order (custom object)
Primary display: invoice_number
```

**1.6 Contact property groups** — Add to native Contact object:
```
Group "Subscription Plan": current_plan (text), plan_price (number),
  billing_interval (enumeration: month/year), period_start (date),
  period_end (date), plan_status (enumeration: active/cancelled/past_due)
Group "Notification Preferences": notify_order_updates (booleancheckbox),
  notify_production_reminders (booleancheckbox), notify_marketing (booleancheckbox)
```

**1.7 HubDB Tables:**
- `subscription_plans` — name, description, price, currency, interval, systems_per_year, features (rich text), is_active, display_order
- `affiliated_locations` — name, country, state, city, address, postal_code, phone, email, website, services_offered, specialties, latitude, longitude, description, logo_url, is_featured, display_order
- `products` — name, slug, description, short_description, price, compare_at_price, currency, category, primary_image (image), in_stock (boolean), featured (boolean), display_order

